SUMMARY:Alvin Ailey American Dance Theater
DTSTAMP:20260321T224050Z
DTSTART:20260322T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Paramount Theatre is located in downtown Seattle at 911 Pin
	e Street\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an 9 ticket limit for this event. 
